GUI OPTIONAL STRING_ENCODED XLSXR_IN_ADDITIONAL_DATETIME_FORMATS_XLSXR_1 Additional Date/Time Format:
DEFAULT_MACRO XLSXR_IN_READ_FORM_CONTROLS_XLSXR_1 NONE
XLSXR_1_READ_FORM_CONTROLS "$(XLSXR_IN_READ_FORM_CONTROLS_XLSXR_1)"
